        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your performances are a call to action for the crowds who listen to you. For 1 hour after you successfully Make an Impression using Performance, you can make a Request of a member of the affected audience using Performance instead of Diplomacy.",
